object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Control Kit by press WASD or the directional arrows. Pressing W/Up makes Kit jump while press S/Down makes him crouch.

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Welcome to Critter Quest! Your character's name is Kit. Try moving through this level before the time runs out!

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: These are Gems and a 1-Up. Collecting a 1-Up will grant you an extra life. Collecting 100 Gems will also give you a extra life.

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Kill enemies by jumping on their heads.

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: This is the exit. Jump into it to unlock the next level.

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Keep an eye open for secret areas! Try jumping on the frog to get back up top.
